==Documentation==
This template creates the individual objects cards that show on the Objects page. The data is passed into this template from Module:FranchiseQuery

===Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description
|-
|| Title || The original game name / path in wiki
|-
|| CleanTitle || The name with Games/ removed
|-
|| Deck || Short description shown in hero
|-
|| Image || Thumbnail image in raw format
|}

===Usage===
<pre>
Called from Module:ObjectQuery not directly used.
</pre>
</noinclude>
<div class="listing-card">
    <div class="listing-card-link" data-url="{{fullurl:{{{url_title}}}}}">
        <div class="listing-card-image clickable-box"><!--
            -->{{#if: {{{image|}}} | 
                {{#ifeq: {{#sub: {{{image|}}} | 0 | 4 }} | http
                | {{{image}}}
                | [[File:{{{image}}}|300px|link=]]
                }}
                | https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/11/110673/3026329-gb_default-16_9.png <!-- Default Fallback -->
                }}
        </div>
        <div class="listing-card-info">
            <div class="listing-card-title clickable-box" role="heading" aria-level="3">{{{title}}}</div>
            <div class="listing-card-deck">{{{deck|}}}</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>